{"title":"我走过这条小路","authors":["胡惠玲"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":9,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我走过这条小路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡惠玲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我走过这条小路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在解放前的一个夜晚；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寻不到一盏灯光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星星也那么暗淡！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹落叶飒飒响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的脚步越发忙乱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昏迷中的母亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在等待着医生诊断。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过荒野越过土岗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小路呵，曲曲弯弯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没等我走完小路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲已经阖上了眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今我背着药包，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又走在这条小路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿叶在头上轻轻拂动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦子在身边唦唦生长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我已经成为公社医生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺小路走遍远近村庄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把欢乐带给劳动的人们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把幸福送进每扇门窗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民和党抚育了我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我天天迎着灿烂阳光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小路也越来越加明亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路边弥漫着一片芬芳！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}